sequenceDiagram
  participant U as user
  participant CLI as CLI entry
  participant H as Harness
  participant M as Model
  participant TR as Tool Runtime
  participant FS as Project environment
  participant S as Session Store

  U->>CLI: Fix failed tests
  CLI->>H: Create or restore a session
  H->>S: Read history, rules, budget
  H->>M: Send current round context
  M-->>H: Return tool intent
  H->>H: Verify permissions and parameters
  H->>TR: execution controlled tools
  TR->>FS: Read files or run tests
  FS-->>TR: Return results
  TR-->>H: observation
  H->>S: Append event log
  H->>M: Next round of context
